    <section id="thecourses" class="container thecourses"> 
     <h2>My Favorite Course</h2> 
     <blockquote>
      <p>“I was able to listen to Chinese spoken in film and understand what was being discussed. Through movies I was also able to observe Chinese culture and values.”</p>
     </blockquote> 
     <p class="name"><strong>Jessica Cooney</strong> on Selected Topics in Modern Chinese Literature and Film</p> 
